{"about_the_game":"X-Force Under Attack brings back all the charm of shmup games from the 80's/90's. It's a frenetic and chaotic space shooter with insane battles against extremely difficult bosses. Embark on epic battles and stop enemies from establishing a military base orbiting the planet Genesis<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bullet Hell</h2><br>Defeat several enemies and hundreds of projectiles, coming from all sides at the same time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/Bullet_Hell.gif?t=1697840617\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Ships</h2><br>Select the ship that best suits you. Each ship has unique attributes that make it best for a specific player type and stage, so choose wisely.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/Select_Ship.gif?t=1697840617\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bosses</h2><br>Fight gigantic, intimidating bosses, each one more difficult than the last, and defeat them to end an era of tyranny.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446740/extras/Boss10.gif?t=1697840617\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure through 10 beautiful and unique levels.<br></li><li>Defeat the gigantic bosses spread throughout space.<br></li><li>Make upgrades to your ship to be able to fight and defeat enemies.<br></li><li>Use Power-ups to annihilate various shots and enemies on the screen.<br></li><li>Dodge comets lost in space<br></li><li>And much more.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Trophy - Super Power Shot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2446740/445ac8e104cc1101641a9ae0c40cdaf3d970f07a.jpg"},{"name":"Trophy - Shield Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2446740/9e3aca114a8b61566f47ca290eaa187cbd12c791.jpg"},{"name":"Trophy - Drone","path":"https://cdn.